label: Chronometric Age Conversion Protocol (IRI)
rdfs_comment: The method used to convert the uncalibratedChronometricAge into a chronometric age in years, as captured in maximumChronometricAge, maximumChronometricAgeReferenceSystem, minimumChronometricAge, and minimumChronometricAgeReferenceSystem.
dcterms_description: Terms in the chronoiri namespace are intended to be used in RDF with non-literal objects.

label: Chronometric Age Determined By (IRI)

label: Chronometric Age Protocol (IRI)
